                <head>25. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d25fn1">Source: Carter Library, Brzezinski
                        Donated Material, Subject File, Box 27, Meetings–20: 7/7/77. Secret. The
                        meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. Minutes of the meeting
                        were not found.</note>
                </head>
